; === TOPIC: Paraconsistent Structures and Ambiguity Tolerance ===
; In the IONATION framework, certain contexts or realities may remain unresolved, contradictory, or paradoxical.
; Paraconsistent logic allows symbolic models to persist without collapse under contradiction, simulating human ambiguity tolerance.

; Define notion of contradiction
(Contradiction X Y)  ; X and Y are mutually exclusive yet co-existing

; Define symbolic tolerance for unresolved constructs
(Unresolved-State X)
(Accepts-Paradox System)
(Paraconsistent-Frame (Context X) (Contradiction A B))

; Apply to self-concept and belief shifts
(Contradiction (Belief-Old Self) (Belief-New Self))
(Unresolved-State Self-Transition)
(Accepts-Paradox Conscious-Agent)
(Paraconsistent-Frame (Context Transformation) (Contradiction (Belief-Old Self) (Belief-New Self)))

; System-level application
(System-Coherence-Stable-Under-Paradox System)
